WEBVTT

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:02.200
"Mvaa kilemba kama wewe
anafanya nini bungeni kwetu?"

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.616
Sikuwahi kujibu.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:06.736
Ninafuta tu hizo barua.

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:10.920
Nawaza tu kua watumaji
na mimi hatuna mfanano wowote.

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:13.936
Hawakunielewa mimi,

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:16.280
na mimi sikuwaelewa wao.

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:20.976
Ndipo siku moja, mwenzangu mmoja
kwenye bunge akasema

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.540
kua ningetakiwa kutunza barua za chuki.

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:27.820
"Pale kitu kinapokutokea,
itawapa polisi mwongozo."

00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:29.856
(Kicheko)

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:34.326
Niliona kua alisema,
"Pale kitu kinapotokea" na sio "kama."